# Plan 8: Blog System (Frontend)

## Goal
Implement the public-facing blog section with a card layout and rich text rendering.

## Tasks
- [ ] Create `app/blog/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Create `app/blog/[slug]/page.tsx`.
- [ ] Create a `BlogCard` component:
    - [ ] Use **ShadCN Card**.
    - [ ] Use **ShadCN Badge** for tags.
- [ ] Implement reading time estimation.
- [ ] Add social share buttons.
- [ ] Render rich text content:
    - [ ] Use Tailwind Typography (`prose`) or custom styles matching the theme.
